  "content": {
    "prompt": "Construct a program that calculates the base raised to the power of the non-negative exponent without using multiplication.",
    "source_code": "base = 2\nexp = 5\n\nif(exp == 0):\n    print(1)\n\nelse:\n    result = base\n    temp = base\n\n    for i in range(1, exp):\n        for j in range (1, base):\n            result += temp\n        temp = result\n    print(result)"
  },
